Serves 2-4 people 
1 small eggplant
1small zucchini
3 cloves of garlic
½ a bunch of fresh basil , (15g)
1 teaspoon dried oregano
1 teaspoon dried chilli flakes
olive oil
1 tablespoon baby capers
1 tablespoon red wine vinegar
1 x 400 g tin of good quality plum tomatoes
320 g dried wholewheat spaghetti
50 g pecorino/Parmesan or ricotta cheese (for non-vegans) 
extra virgin olive oil

node.text: Hi guys! I realize I never really talk about things that are very personal to me, so I thought in this video I would share a little bit about my modelling journey and my struggle with alcoholism and addiction and how it wasn’t until I decided to accept the help offered to me and do the work on myself that I ended up with a life I never dared to dream of. I hope this video can inspire you to not feel ashamed of asking for help if you are going through something similar, and know that you are not alone, whatever you are going through. All my Love and strength❤️

node.title: A day at a shoot and my modelling story!
